OL,3,CInflation holds steady but markets bet
OL,4,Cagainst August interest rate cut
OL,6,FInflation has remained unchanged and
OL,7,Fstays at the Bank of England's target
OL,8,Frate of 2%, as ITV News Economics
OL,9,FEditor Joel Hills reports
OL,11,FA debate rages about whether Taylor
OL,12,FSwift's UK tour forced up the price of
OL,13,Fhotel rooms in June, however, the Bank
OL,14,Fof England is expected to ignore this
OL,15,Fissue.
OL,17,FPop stars perform and then move on.
OL,18,FThe Bank's concern is that inflation
OL,19,Fin the services sector of the economy
OL,20,Fis hanging around.
