OL,3,CInflation holds steady but markets bet
OL,4,Cagainst August interest rate cut
OL,6,FThe headline annual rate of inflation
OL,7,Fin the UK remained at 2% last month.
OL,9,FBut in the schools, hospitals, hotels,
OL,10,Frestaurants, banks, insurance
OL,11,Fcompanies, law firms, accountants and
OL,12,FIT businesses, which make up the
OL,13,F"services" sector, prices did not
OL,14,Fbehave in a way the Bank of England
OL,15,Fexpected.
OL,17,FThe Bank had annual services inflation
OL,18,Fof 5.1% pencilled in for June.
OL,19,FAccording to the Office for National
OL,20,FStatistics, it ran at 5.7% - that's
OL,21,Fquite a miss.
