OL,3,CInflation holds steady but markets bet
OL,4,Cagainst August interest rate cut
OL,6,FPay is a major chunk of a company's
OL,7,Fcosts. If pay growth is strong and
OL,8,Fproductivity growth weak - which is
OL,9,Fthe case in the UK - then firms are
OL,10,Fmore likely to try to pass their costs
OL,11,Fon, keeping inflation above target.
OL,13,FThe evidence shows this has been
OL,14,Fhappening although the degree to which
OL,15,Fit continues to is up for debate.
