OL,3,CInflation holds steady but markets bet
OL,4,Cagainst August interest rate cut
OL,6,FThe wild upswing in food and energy
OL,7,Finflation drove up the price of almost
OL,8,Feverything in the UK. Food and energy
OL,9,Finflation has since faded but strong
OL,10,Fpay growth is the ripple effect they
OL,11,Fcaused.
OL,13,FTomorrow's Labour Market Day may offer
OL,14,Fmore insight.
