OL,6,FFor now, the Bank may feel tempted to
OL,7,Fkeep interest rates where they are.
OL,8,FNot least as the economy is growing,
OL,9,Fthe housing market looks stable and
OL,10,Fborrowers seem to be finding ways of
OL,11,Fcoping with higher repayments, however
OL,12,Funwelcome.
OL,14,FA week ago, investors were betting on
OL,15,Fa 60% chance of a rate cut in August.
OL,16,FToday they think there's a 60%
OL,17,Fprobability the costs of borrowing
OL,18,Fwill remain where it is.
